
1.  Source the export.sh file

	source export.sh

    This sets up the paths etc needed to 
    use the BDD package.

2.  Run the install script.

	source install.sh


3.  Run the ./build.sh script.

	./build.sh

    There is some problem?  Run it 
    again

	./build.sh

4.  The package is ready to use.  Go to
    the tests/ directory and look at
    hello_world.c



4.  At any point, for more information, type
	(assuming you are in this directory)

	man -M ./man bdd

